# Tech stack (required)

Use **only** these technologies for new work in this repo. Do not introduce alternate frameworks, languages, or duplicate libraries.

## Core

| Area | Choice |
|------|--------|
| Language | **JavaScript** (`.js` / `.jsx`) — **no** `.ts` / `.tsx` source files |
| Runtime | **Node.js 18+** |
| Package manager | **npm** with **workspaces** (`packages/*` for shared libs; app lives at repo root) |
| UI | **React 18** |
| Build | **Vite 6** + `@vitejs/plugin-react` |
| Routing | **React Router 7** — import from `@/lib/router` (`Link`, `BrowserRouter`, `Routes`, `useNavigate`, etc.) |
| Server state | **TanStack Query (React Query) v5** — `@tanstack/react-query` |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS 3** + PostCSS + Autoprefixer + `tailwindcss-animate` |
| Components / a11y | **Radix UI** primitives (shadcn-style under `src/components/ui/`) |
| Forms | **React Hook Form** + **Zod** + `@hookform/resolvers` |
| Icons | **lucide-react** |
| Charts | **recharts** |
| Motion | **framer-motion** |
| Toasts | **sonner** — use `import { toast } from "sonner"`; do not add `react-hot-toast` |
| PDF / screenshots | **jspdf**, **html2canvas** |
| Theming | **next-themes** |
| Env | **Vite** env vars only — prefix `VITE_*`, read via `import.meta.env` |

## Patterns

- Path alias: `@/*` → `src/*` (see `jsconfig.json`).
- New pages: register in `src/pages.config.js`; use functional components and hooks.
- Data fetching: prefer TanStack Query (`useQuery` / `useMutation`) over ad-hoc `useEffect` fetch.
- Do not add TypeScript, Vue, Angular, Next.js App Router, Redux, or alternate CSS-in-JS unless explicitly approved.

## Examples

```jsx
// Routing (Vite SPA)
import { Link, useNavigate } from "@/lib/router";

// Query
import { useQuery } from "@tanstack/react-query";

// Toast
import { toast } from "sonner";

// Env
const apiUrl = import.meta.env.VITE_BASE44_BACKEND_URL;
```
